    <entry>
      <title>栈，链表，队列 简单实现</title>
      <link href="posts/c12a.html"/>
      <url>posts/c12a.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="栈，链表，队列-简单实现"><a href="#栈，链表，队列-简单实现" class="headerlink" title="栈，链表，队列 简单实现"></a>栈，链表，队列 简单实现</h1><h2 id="1-栈"><a href="#1-栈" class="headerlink" title="1. 栈"></a>1. 栈</h2><h3 id="1-1-数组实现"><a href="#1-1-数组实现" class="headerlink" title="1.1 数组实现"></a>1.1 数组实现</h3><p><strong>代码思路:</strong></p><ul><li>maxSize ：栈的大小（数组的大小）</li><li>stack：用来模拟栈的数组</li><li>top ：指向当前栈顶元素，初始值为 -1 ，表示栈空</li><li>判断栈满：<strong>top == maxSize - 1</strong> ，即已经到达数组最后一个位置</li><li>判断栈空：<strong>top == -1</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> com.kuang;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * <span class="doctag">@author</span> xiaokuangshen</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * <span class="doctag">@date</span> 2020/11/29</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">ArrayStackDemo</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">// 定义一个内部类 实现数组栈</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">ArrayStack</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> maxSize; <span class="comment">// 栈的大小</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[] stack; <span class="comment">// 存放栈的数组</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">//因为数组第一个数据下标从0开始</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> top = -<span class="number">1</span>; <span class="comment">// 栈顶赋值为 -1</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">          * 构造数组栈</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">          * 构造一个长度为 maxSize 的数组</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">          *</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">          * <span class="doctag">@param</span> maxSize 栈的大小</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">          */</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title">ArrayStack</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> maxSize)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">this</span>.maxSize = maxSize;</span><br><span class="line">             stack = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[<span class="keyword">this</span>.maxSize];</span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">// 判断栈是否为满</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">boolean</span> <span class="title">isFull</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">return</span> top == maxSize - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">// 判断栈是否为空</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">boolean</span> <span class="title">isEmpty</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">return</span> top == -<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">// 入栈</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">push</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> value)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="comment">// 先判断栈空间是否还有空余</span></span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">if</span> (isFull()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                 System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;栈满,不能再进去了&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">                 <span class="keyword">return</span>; <span class="comment">//目的是当条件成立时不执行后面的语句</span></span><br><span class="line">             &#125;</span><br><span class="line">             top++;</span><br><span class="line">             stack[top] = value;</span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">// 出栈</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">pop</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="comment">// 先判断栈空间是否为空</span></span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">if</span> (isEmpty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                 <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> RuntimeException(<span class="string">&quot;没有东西,还删除什么?&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">             &#125;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">int</span> value = stack[top];</span><br><span class="line">             top--;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">return</span> value;</span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">// 遍历</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">show</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="comment">// 先判断栈空间是否为空</span></span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">if</span> (isEmpty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                 <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> RuntimeException(<span class="string">&quot;没有东西,还遍历什么?&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">             &#125;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="comment">//注意 i &gt;= 0 因为数组下标从0开始 从栈顶开始遍历</span></span><br><span class="line">             <span class="comment">//先进后出</span></span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = top; i &gt;= <span class="number">0</span>; i--) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                 System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;stack[&quot;</span>+i+<span class="string">&quot;]= &quot;</span>+stack[i]);</span><br><span class="line">             &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">// 定义一个大小为5的数组栈</span></span><br><span class="line">        ArrayStack stack = <span class="keyword">new</span> ArrayStack(<span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//添加数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        stack.push(<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        stack.push(<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        stack.push(<span class="number">3</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        stack.push(<span class="number">4</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        stack.push(<span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//多添加一个数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        stack.push(<span class="number">6</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        stack.show();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//出栈</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> pop = stack.pop();</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;出栈的是: &quot;</span>+pop);</span><br><span class="line">        stack.show();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-链表"><a href="#2-链表" class="headerlink" title="2. 链表"></a>2. 链表</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> com.kuang;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * <span class="doctag">@author</span> xiaokuangshen</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * <span class="doctag">@date</span> 2020/11/29 15:31</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">TLinkedList</span>&lt;<span class="title">T</span>&gt; </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Node head;<span class="comment">//链表头部</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> size;<span class="comment">//链表元素的个数</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title">TLinkedList</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        head=<span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        size=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//    将结点作为内部类。也可以新建一个Node类，作为结点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Node</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> Node next;<span class="comment">//下一个结点</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> T t;<span class="comment">//结点的数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title">Node</span><span class="params">(T t)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">this</span>.t=t;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> T <span class="title">getT</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> t;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">setT</span><span class="params">(T t)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">this</span>.t = t;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//    在链表头部添加一个结点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">addFirst</span><span class="params">(T t)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Node node = <span class="keyword">new</span> Node(t);</span><br><span class="line">        node.next=head;</span><br><span class="line">        head=node;</span><br><span class="line">        size++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//    在链表中间添加一个结点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">addMid</span><span class="params">(T t,<span class="keyword">int</span> index)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Node node = <span class="keyword">new</span> Node(t);</span><br><span class="line">        Node mid=head;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; index - <span class="number">1</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            mid=mid.next;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        node.next=mid.next;</span><br><span class="line">        mid.next=node;</span><br><span class="line">        size++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//    在链表尾部添加一个结点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">addLast</span><span class="params">(T t)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Node node = <span class="keyword">new</span> Node(t);</span><br><span class="line">        Node last=head;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (last.next!=<span class="keyword">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            last=last.next;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        last.next=node;</span><br><span class="line">        node.next=<span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        size++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//    删除链表的头结点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">removeFirst</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        head=head.next;</span><br><span class="line">        size--;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//    删除链表的中间元素</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">removeMid</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> index)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Node mid=head;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (index==<span class="number">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            removeFirst();</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> j=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        Node qMid=head;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (j&lt;index)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            qMid=mid;</span><br><span class="line">            mid=mid.next;</span><br><span class="line">            j++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        qMid.next=mid.next;</span><br><span class="line">        size--;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//    删除链表的尾结点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">removeLast</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Node mid=head;</span><br><span class="line">        Node qMid=head;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (mid.next!=<span class="keyword">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            qMid=mid;</span><br><span class="line">            mid=mid.next;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        qMid.next= <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        size--;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//    获取链表指定下标的结点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> Node <span class="title">get</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> index)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Node mid=head;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (index==<span class="number">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> head;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> j=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (j&lt;index)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            mid=mid.next;</span><br><span class="line">            j++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> mid;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        TLinkedList&lt;String&gt; linkedList = <span class="keyword">new</span> TLinkedList&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">        linkedList.addFirst(<span class="string">&quot;hello1&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        linkedList.addFirst(<span class="string">&quot;hello2&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        linkedList.addFirst(<span class="string">&quot;hello3&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; linkedList.size; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            System.out.println(linkedList.get(i).getT());</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//        linkedList.removeLast();</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//        linkedList.removeFirst();</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//        linkedList.addLast(&quot;hello4&quot;);</span></span><br><span class="line">        linkedList.addMid(<span class="string">&quot;hello&quot;</span>,<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;--------------&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; linkedList.size; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            System.out.println(linkedList.get(i).getT());</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-队列"><a href="#3-队列" class="headerlink" title="3. 队列"></a>3. 队列</h2><h3 id="3-1-数组实现"><a href="#3-1-数组实现" class="headerlink" title="3.1 数组实现"></a>3.1 数组实现</h3><p><strong>代码思路:</strong></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> com.kuang;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * <span class="doctag">@author</span> xiaokuangshen</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * <span class="doctag">@date</span> 2020/11/29 19:49</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">ArrayQueueDemo</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 编写内部类实现 数组队列</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">ArrayQueue</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> maxSize; <span class="comment">// 队列大小</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[] queue; <span class="comment">//数组队列 保存数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> front; <span class="comment">//头结点</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> rear; <span class="comment">//尾结点</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//构造一个长度为 value 的数组队列</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title">ArrayQueue</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> value)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            maxSize = value;</span><br><span class="line">            queue = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[maxSize];</span><br><span class="line">            front = -<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            rear = -<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 判断数组队列是否满了</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> Boolean <span class="title">isFull</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span>  rear == maxSize - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 判断数组队列是否为空</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> Boolean <span class="title">isEmpty</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> rear == front;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 添加数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">add</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> value)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 先判断数组队列是否还有空间存放数据</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (isFull())&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;没空间了，不要加了啦...&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span>; <span class="comment">// 阻止后面语句执行</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            rear++;</span><br><span class="line">            queue[rear] = value;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 出队列</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">put</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 先判断数组队列是否为空</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(isEmpty())&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> RuntimeException(<span class="string">&quot;没东西了，不要往外面掏了...&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            front++;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> queue[front];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 遍历队列</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">show</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 先判断数组队列是否为空</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(isEmpty())&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> RuntimeException(<span class="string">&quot;没东西了，不要往外面掏了...&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = front + <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= rear; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;queue[&quot;</span>+i+<span class="string">&quot;]= &quot;</span>+queue[i]);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        ArrayQueue queue = <span class="keyword">new</span> ArrayQueue(<span class="number">3</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//添加数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        queue.add(<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        queue.add(<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        queue.add(<span class="number">3</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 多添加</span></span><br><span class="line">        queue.add(<span class="number">4</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        queue.show();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//出队列</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> put = queue.put();</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;出队列的是: &quot;</span>+put);</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;============&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        queue.show();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://gitee.com/white_maple/picgo-image/raw/master/img/20210528111559.png" alt="image-20210528111551956"></p>]]></content>
      
      
